package.name: swoole
package.summary: Event-driven asynchronous and concurrent networking engine with high performance for PHP.
package.description: Event-driven asynchronous and concurrent networking engine with high performance for PHP. - event-driven - coroutine - asynchronous non-blocking - multi-thread reactor - multi-process worker - multi-protocol - millisecond timer - built-in tcp/http/websocket/http2 server - coroutine tcp/http/websocket client - coroutine read/write file system - coroutine dns lookup - support IPv4/IPv6/UnixSocket/TCP/UDP - support SSL/TLS encrypted transmission
package.notes: - Fixed a compilation failure caused by missing `zlib` dependency. - Optimized the resource management logic in the `curl` module to prevent use-after-free risks. - Resolved the absence of `fdatasync` on macOS systems. - Improved the log output format for coroutine deadlock detection.

configureoption.name: enable-swoole-thread
configureoption.prompt: enable swoole thread support (need php zts support)?
